73
00:09:46,408 --> 00:09:47,076
Le double-burger.

74
00:09:53,750 --> 00:09:55,711
Chuck ! J'ai pris un double-burger !

75
00:09:55,879 --> 00:09:57,923
Ta gueule ! Je le sais, j'étais là !

76
