Mais tu le savais !

81
00:10:07,391 --> 00:10:09,267
Fais pas le con, passe-le-moi.

82
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:12,480
Alors, tu me files tes 16 cents,

83
00:10:12,647 --> 00:10:13,982
